sourcesContent:
let searchInputStyle = {
  width: "100%",
  height: "30px",
  outlineWidth: "0px",
  boxSizing: "border-box",
  fontSize: "17px"
}

let listContainerStyle = {
  display: "inline-block",
  width: "200px", 
  height: "85vh", 
  overflowY: "scroll"
}

let searchTypeDeviceStyle = {
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  width: "66px",
  height: "27px",
  borderRadius: "5px 0px 0px 5px",
  textAlign: "center",
  paddingTop: "3px",
  cursor: "pointer",
  userSelect: "none"
}

let searchTypeUserStyle = {
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  width: "66px",
  height: "27px",
  margin: "0px 2px 0px 2px",
  textAlign: "center",
  paddingTop: "3px",
  cursor: "pointer",
  userSelect: "none"
}

let searchTypeDeviceStyleHighlight = {
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  width: "62px",
  height: "25px",
  borderRadius: "5px 0px 0px 5px",
  textAlign: "center",
  borderStyle: "solid",
  borderColor: "black",
  borderWidth: "2px",
  paddingTop: "1px",
  cursor: "pointer",
  userSelect: "none"
}

let searchTypeUserStyleHighlight = {
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  width: "62px",
  height: "25px",
  textAlign: "center",
  borderStyle: "solid",
  borderColor: "black",
  borderWidth: "2px",
  margin: "0px 0px 0px 2px",
  paddingTop: "1px",
  cursor: "pointer",
  userSelect: "none"
}


export {
  searchInputStyle,
  listContainerStyle,
  searchTypeDeviceStyle,
  searchTypeUserStyle,
  searchTypeDeviceStyleHighlight,
  searchTypeUserStyleHighlight
}
